title: GAME OF THRONES Season 8 Episode 6 Breakdown, Recap and Theories | The Iron Throne | Final Episode
author: Think Story
comment: So I may have vented a bit...
The Unsullied and Dothraki kinda forgot they all died at Winterfell
Legend says Drogon is still looking for the writers
The memes from this final season will be more epic than the season itself.
Drogon had the best, most logical, and impactful moment in the whole episode.
description:
In this breakdown we take a look at Game of Thrones Season 8 Episode 6, the final and last episode, recapping and reviewing why I think this is the death of the show. Is the writing as bad as others make it out to be?
